    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices with which pages of a book or other materials can be turned without the use of hands. With variations in design these may be used to assist reading for the disabled, for musicians reading musical scores, or to photographically duplicate books.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
